<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الْقَصَصِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ طسم الْقَصَصِ وَهِيَ مَكِّيَّةٌ كُلُّهَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{طسم {١}</span> تِلْكَ آيَاتُ الْكِتَابِ الْمُبِينِ <span class="c3">{٢}</span> } <span class="c4">[القصص: ١-٢]</span> وَقَدْ فَسَّرْنَاهُ فِي طسم الشُّعَرَاءِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ عَزَّ وَجَلَّ:</span> <span class="c3">{نَتْلُوا عَلَيْكَ مِنْ نَبَإِ مُوسَى}</span> <span class="c4">[القصص: ٣]</span> مِنْ خَبَرِ مُوسَى.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{وَفِرْعَوْنَ بِالْحَقِّ لِقَوْمٍ يُؤْمِنُونَ}</span> <span class="c4">[القصص: ٣]</span> لِقَوْمٍ يُصَدِّقُونَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{إِنَّ فِرْعَوْنَ عَلا فِي الأَرْضِ}</span> <span class="c4">[القصص: ٤]</span> قَالَ قَتَادَةُ: بَغَى فِي الأَرْضِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ السُّدِّيُّ:</span> يَعْنِي: أَرْضَ مِصْرَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَجَعَلَ أَهْلَهَا شِيَعًا}</span> <span class="c4">[القصص: ٤]</span> قَالَ قَتَادَةُ: أَيْ: فِرَقًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>